data.description: This charming all-brick 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom rancher nestled in the heart of Halls is an absolute gem. Upon entering, you're greeted by a generously open living and dining area, complemented by a cozy breakfast bar. The master suite boasts a private full bath and a spacious walk-in closet. Enjoy the delightful fenced yard featuring a covered porch, ideal for grilling or unwinding by the fire pit. Whether you envision it as your dream home or a savvy long-term rental investment, don't miss the chance to make it yours - contact your agent now to schedule a showing!
